ity furniture for 78 years — founded in 1946, now run by the third generation of our family. Today, Greg and his family continue that legacy through Bad Ass Recliners, a business built on quality craftsmanship, excellent customer service, and a passion for creating something truly unique.<\/p><p>We believe in building our reputation one recliner at a time — no shortcuts, no compromises. In an industry where true American-made furniture is increasingly rare, we take pride in offering products that you’ll be proud to have in your home and that will last for generations.<\/p><p>Bad Ass Recliners brings a bold new dimension to our tradition of craftsmanship. From our signature whiskey barrel and wine barrel recliners to a wide variety of other exciting styles, every piece is designed to stand out — and stand the test of time. We offer an extensive selection of fabrics and leathers, including new durable, cleanable materials, so you can choose the perfect design to suit your space.<\/p><p>At the heart of it all, we’re a family business that believes in community, integrity, and treating every customer like family. Give us a try — you’ll be glad you did!<\/p><p>— Greg<\/p>","large_text":false}}},"block_order":["circular_text_xNqnNz","heading_i3KjWQ","text_wA6qez"],"settings":{"section_width":"container","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Screenshot_2025-06-09_at_9.39.06_AM.png","media_size":"adapt","show_image_2":true,"image_2":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/IMG_0605.jpg","position_image_2":"bottom-right","media_size_2":"adapt","desktop_image_width":"50","use_video":false,"video":"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=_9VUPq3SxOc","video_autoplay":true,"video_controls":true,"layout":"left","column_gap":"16","vertical_alignment":"center","content_alignment":"start","bg_color":"","text_color":"","bg_column":"","padding_top":100,"padding_bottom":100}},"media_grid_kqmDrT":{"type":"media-grid","blocks":{"media_J3RxBd":{"type":"media","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Screen